2. cs.RO - The paper also mentions the use of BTs in the robotics industry, which falls under the category of Robotics (RO). 
3. cs.SY - The paper deals with synchronization techniques to tackle concurrency problems in BTs, which is a common topic in the field of Systems and Control (SY). 
4. cs.SE - The paper discusses design choices and their impact on execution performance, which is a common topic in the field of Software Engineering (SE). 
5. cs.PL - The paper deals with the composition of behaviors using BTs, which is a common topic in the field of Programming Languages (PL).
